We can see that we have a serviceaccount.yaml file inside the k8 folder in the demo repository, this created the SA we need to run all the microservices using the deploy.yaml file, otherwise it would start using the default SA 
provided by the k8
code base:- 
---
apiVersion: v1
kind: ServiceAccount
metadata:
  name: opentelemetry-demo
  labels:

    opentelemetry.io/name: opentelemetry-demo
    app.kubernetes.io/instance: opentelemetry-demo
    app.kubernetes.io/name: opentelemetry-demo
    app.kubernetes.io/version: "1.12.0"
    app.kubernetes.io/part-of: opentelemetry-demo
